-> Storing past results to reduce expensive computation
-> Recursion + storing your past results

int knapsack(int wt[],int profit,int W,int N){
    if(n==0 || W==0)    ; base-case
        return 0;
        
    int result;
        
    if(wt[n]>W)         ; decision-space tree
        return knapsack(wt,profit,W,N-1);
        
    else
        result = max(knapsack(wt,profit,W,N-1),knapsack(wt,profit,W-w[N],N-1);)
    return mem[W][N] = result;
}

Time Complexity = O(nxW)


Problems:
-> Space wasted
-> Stack Overflow
